-- CSN Mine Expansion May Slow on Preservation Effort, Valor Says
-- B y   P e t e r   M i l l a r d
-- 2011-12-16T12:02:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-16/csn-mine-expansion-may-slow-on-preservation-effort-valor-says.html
 Cia.  Siderurgica Nacional (CSNA3)  SA may
have to slow expansion at its Casa de Pedra iron-ore mine as
authorities seek to protect an area near the mine as a
historical site, Valor Economico reported, citing Anderson
Cabido, the mayor of Congonhas, where the mine is located.  To contact the reporter on this story:
